cards.backMarkdown:
(1) It appeals to prurient interests (sexually stimulating): average person standard (how would the average person, applying community standards, view the material as a whole?);
(2) It is patently offensive in its sexual portrayal:
  (i) material must offend community standards regarding portrayal of sexual matters;
  (ii) any law prohibiting obscene material must specify what is deemed patently offensive;
(3) Taken as a whole, the material lacks serious literary, artistic, political, or scientific value: determined based on national standard (not community standard, as is the case for first two prongs).

