  (1) Rights, duties, & obligations:
    (i) General partners: manage and control day-to-day operations; owe the same fiduciary duties as partners in a general partnership;
    (ii) Limited partners: usually passive investors with limited authority; no fiduciary duties owed to partnership; unless partnership agreement provides otherwise, may compete and/or have interests adverse to partnerships;
