    (i) General partners: personally, jointly, and severally liable for all partnership obligations; incoming partners are not liable for obligations the partnership incurred before they became general partners;
    (ii) Limited partners: liable only to the extent of their investment;
  (3) Formation: filing a certificate of limited partnership with the state; certificate must generally contain names and addresses of each general partner and their signatures.
